#security-bg
  %section.security
    %h3 We're serious about security
    .large-4.columns
      =image_tag('landing/shield.svg')
      %h5 Best-in-class encryption
      %p
        We use AES 256-bit SSL to encrypt your traffic and sync your balances between your iOS devices and the secure server.

    .large-4.columns
      =image_tag('landing/oink.svg')
      %h5 We can't access your money
      %p
        We use the
        =link_to 'public blockchain', 'https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Block_chain', target: '_blank'
        to derive balance and transaction data, never your private keys. No one can access your money using the data you share with us.

    .large-4.columns
      =image_tag('landing/love.svg')
      %h5 We'll never sell your data
      %p
        We love our customers. We only make money from iOS app sales, non-tracking website ads, and
        =link_to 'donations.', 'bitcoin:12Rzu1UsUFnBFcdCicDp6VKc9JhRLum3TD'
        We don't sell
        %u any
        user data to anyone, and we never will.

#currencies-bg
  %section.currencies
    %article
      =image_tag('landing/available-coins.svg')

%section
